@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_kydwdc(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (0.07 + wp.exp((v0 + 0.54 / v1 + 0.17)))
    v2 = ((wp.sin(tmp + 0.43) - wp.cos(v1 + 0.95)) - v2)
    tmp = (tmp * ((v2 + 0.86 + tmp + 0.38) + (v2 + 0.67 / tmp + 0.33)))
    v0 = wp.exp(0.12)
    v2 = 0.60
    v1 = (0.89 / v1)
    v2 = ((0.45 / (v1 + 0.76 / v1 + 0.50)) * v2)
    v1 = v0
    data[tid] = v0
